    <section xml:id="Header-Identity-Mapping-Introduction">
        <title>Introduction</title>
        <para>With the Header Identity Mapping Filter, Repose can introspect a configured Header and set the X-PP-User
            and X-PP-Groups headers accordingly.
        </para>
